Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.40,0:00:06.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被扔在了社團室的門口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.29,0:00:09.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都還這麼小
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:12.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.57,0:00:13.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.33,0:00:17.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}毛髮被梳理得那麼整理 一定是走散了

Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.53,0:02:09.26,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\pos(1095,580)}{\pos(980,560)}{\3c&HB58E00&}{\fn方正综艺_GBK\fs40\fad(500,300)}小貓的黑與白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:01:58.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這些孩子 不能由喵咪部代為撫養嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.33,0:02:05.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喵咪部的活動宗旨是將受傷或在鎮子離迷路的動物放歸自然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.42,0:02:09.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算暫時照顧 目的也不是為了飼養
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.28,0:02:11.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:14.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有誰能養這些小貓咪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:16.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我家因為是公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.30,0:02:19.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我家白天沒有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.96,0:02:22.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那段時間沒辦法照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:25.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔也只是寄住在這裡而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:31.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽前輩家也已經養了兩隻貓 沒辦法再養了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:32.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:39.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣的話 只能由我來養了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.71,0:02:40.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:44.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是已經沒有其他人可以養了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:45.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.63,0:02:49.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大家一起找願意飼養它們的家庭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:52.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在那之前暫時寄存在這沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:59.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是呢 我也贊成天羽前輩的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:02.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔會四處詢問的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.56,0:03:05.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也幫忙問問看好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.40,0:03:06.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:23.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}貓嗎 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.96,0:03:25.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我家稍微有點不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:26.70,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.09,0:03:28.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其他的男生也問了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:32.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已經都問了 你是最後一個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:35.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不行 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:38.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那邊形勢看起來也很嚴峻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:40.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼說 男生也是了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.06,0:03:42.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一個都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:46.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這也是 突然被問到要不要養小貓…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:51.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我稍微去看下情況
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:58.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 美羽前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了 新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:04.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}稍微對小貓有些在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:09.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是 不一直看著就會擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:13.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 它們在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.74,0:04:18.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個是讓小貓咪能夠喝奶的技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:21.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}像這樣 擠壓乳房的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:24.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}乳汁就容易吸出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:25.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:28.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就可能是想起它們母親的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:34.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你 小熊喵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:37.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}做母親代理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:43.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是我能給它們喂奶就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,0:04:44.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:47.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:50.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你剛剛想像了H的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.49,0:04:56.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}突然間做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:58.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好煩給我閉嘴 新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.70,0:05:01.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}像你這樣的傢伙就該這樣 這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:05.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小紗凪也直呼新吾其名了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:06.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:09.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瓜生…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:14.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 你太用力了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:16.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}更慢點推
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.72,0:05:18.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的好的 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:23.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 既找不到飼主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:26.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又被美羽前輩誤解了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:29.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}全部都是新吾的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:33.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小貓們沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:38.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們也不能一直照顧著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:41.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學校裡也有安潔在 還有小熊喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.89,0:05:45.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能找到飼主就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:53.26,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}實在不行的話 就由我來照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.86,0:05:56.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是美羽前輩不是反對了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.74,0:05:57.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:05:58.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:02.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 現在才發現
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:04.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽前輩的手…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.35,0:06:06.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:08.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你知道的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.15,0:06:15.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道的 只是其中的一個傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:19.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}作為考生來到結女的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:21.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}第一次見到了美羽前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:29.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瓜生…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:31.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:33.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:34.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:40.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:44.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不會做危險的事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:55.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瓜生…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:56.70,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.58,0:07:02.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這孩子今天才被我照顧 還沒和人親近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:06.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}肯定是受到很多的傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:08.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}變得不相信人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:11.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:16.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}認真地面對它 和它說話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.78,0:07:18.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的心意就一定能夠傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.89,0:07:22.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你不痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:27.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只要這孩子能夠放心 這點痛不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:33.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我非常吃驚 那肯定是很痛才對的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:35.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但還那麼做…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:39.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}此外 那傷口的數量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:44.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那樣的事情一定是重複了無數次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:47.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個人 就是那種性格的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:52.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為了他人的幸福 而犧牲自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.19,0:07:59.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我因為憧憬那樣的她 也加入了喵咪部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:04.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過 我沒適應那麼做就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:11.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好偉大的一個人啊 美羽前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:22.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你… 對美羽前輩怎麼看的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:23.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:26.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不會生氣的 你說說看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:30.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其實是為了前輩 才加入這個社團的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:33.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那樣的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:37.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}僅僅是因為美羽前輩是一個值得尊敬的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:40.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也想著能多幫助她一些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:42.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其它的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:44.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其它的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.13,0:08:47.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜歡 或者討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.14,0:08:51.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}戀愛的感情 這種類型的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.37,0:08:55.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是說謊的話 估計會被你踢飛的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:08:58.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算你不說 也踢就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:08:59.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:11.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前輩該怎麼說呢 在身邊就能很讓自己安心的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:14.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然不能說得很準確
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:19.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣啊 那我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:20.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:25.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們像這樣一起盪鞦韆 你就沒感覺出什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:29.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:32.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}需要想那麼久嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:36.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被治癒呀 心怦怦直跳呀 有很多的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:39.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可能 如果我是女人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:42.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能和紗凪成為好朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:44.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是這樣的感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:46.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:56.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那樣的話 就做我第一個男性朋友給我看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.74,0:10:06.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.95,0:10:19.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然安潔這個時間也不會在了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:23.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:25.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:29.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:33.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想看看小貓咪怎麼樣了 沒想到美羽…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:38.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:41.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:42.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.06,0:10:45.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你昨晚睡在這裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:47.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不會打工回來就這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:53.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起 因為擔心小貓咪們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:57.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但就這樣睡的話 會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:10:59.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:03.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔馬上端熱騰騰的早飯過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:11.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:15.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:21.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.23,0:11:26.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道前輩是真心愛護動物的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:31.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是不要全部想著一個人承擔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.39,0:11:34.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然可能還幫不上什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:36.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是也讓我 即便只是些許
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:39.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}幫前輩的忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:45.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你 新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:11:59.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哇 好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:00.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:02.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:04.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.94,0:12:07.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:15.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽前輩找到飼主了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:18.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不太好找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.48,0:12:20.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:26.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個… 美羽前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:29.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我能問一件事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:31.25,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.67,0:12:37.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前輩… 對新吾怎麼看的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:40.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:44.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是沒想過就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:55.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯… 在身邊就能讓自己很安心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:57.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:04.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在身邊就能很讓自己安心的人 吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:11.26,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:12.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:16.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那小紗凪怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:17.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:21.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小紗凪對新吾怎麼看的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:24.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:29.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對我來說 新吾是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:36.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:40.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.93,0:13:42.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:45.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喜歡撫慰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.37,0:13:47.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.86,0:13:53.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在打掃的時候 偶然間叫了瓜生的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:55.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這孩子就有了反應
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:59.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像是很喜歡這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:02.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一直都沒有名字 也太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:05.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那這孩子的名字 就叫新吾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:09.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}覺得真是讓人不愉快的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:12.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那這邊這隻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}莫非還是要用誰的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:17.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}愛理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:18.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:20.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.91,0:14:22.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:26.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:27.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.81,0:14:28.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:30.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.96,0:14:33.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是這孩子喜歡那是沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:34.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是有些不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:36.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:45.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 能喜歡美羽前輩的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:47.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這傢伙有著很好的品味嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:51.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}比起來 黑的那隻一點品味都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:52.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.17,0:14:58.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 八冢老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:14:59.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:01.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}稍微耽誤大家一下可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:06.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}照顧被丟棄的小貓是沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:13.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我擔心的問題是 會不會還有新的動物被丟棄給喵咪部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:18.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是這樣的事情再繼續發生 也會對學園造成困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:21.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對於這方面的問題 你們怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.93,0:15:24.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等等 又打算刁難我們了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:26.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是刁難
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:30.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我只是想知道你們是否認真考慮過這個問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:33.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在社團教室的門口貼警示
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:35.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是必然的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:38.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}警示由我來做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:39.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:41.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:42.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:44.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}僅僅是這樣 可能不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:49.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不能給學園造成困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:54.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我就算半夜監視著 也要堅決杜絕類似的事情發生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:56.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}作為喵咪部部長的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:15:59.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前輩 所以就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:00.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 沒事...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:04.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣啊 前輩就是擔心這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:06.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以昨天晚上在社團…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.46,0:16:10.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然我是無法戰勝的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:13.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}半夜的監視 我可不贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:19.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是讓我知道你們有去思考過這個問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:23.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總之你們先試著實行看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:28.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對動物負責任 這才是喵咪部嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:29.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:35.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽前輩 昨晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.48,0:16:39.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你看 果然部長是有責任的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:42.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.22,0:16:47.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天沒有打工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:49.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:52.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那今天放學 就回家去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.37,0:16:55.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}偶爾也要讓身體休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:56.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.90,0:17:01.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我會好好照顧小貓咪和其它動物的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.99,0:17:05.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前輩要是生病了 不是就得不償失了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:08.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我什麼都會去做的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:11.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真溫柔啊 新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:12.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:13.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.58,0:17:25.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在看什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:28.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:31.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:40.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請走好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.03,0:17:44.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}走好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:48.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的是好頑固啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:51.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 你聽到了嗎 美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:56.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別用這樣的眼神看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:18:00.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的新吾 好像要哭一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:06.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:10.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.43,0:18:12.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:15.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 紗凪 看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.41,0:18:16.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:24.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼就不能是紗凪呢 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:29.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:31.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你剛剛看到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:32.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}聽到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:35.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:39.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼事都沒有 別…別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:40.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.62,0:18:46.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}精神飽滿嗎 美羽 新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:49.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:52.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽前輩今天回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.33,0:18:55.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這段時間都一直在勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:57.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想著讓她休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:01.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前輩的話 去打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:02.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.27,0:19:08.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像是突然的通知 才剛剛出門
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.38,0:19:08.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:13.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}像是沒有其他人了 怎麼都不好拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:16.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算這樣 也不用由美羽前輩來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:18.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看起來像是真的遇上麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.45,0:19:21.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}打工結束後 我馬上就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:23.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.74,0:19:25.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不可以的 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:26.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你太勉強自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.99,0:19:28.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學園長不是也說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.03,0:19:31.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喵咪部對動物有責任
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:34.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}特別是作為部長的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.93,0:19:41.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前輩真的是很頑固啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.92,0:19:43.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:50.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.55,0:19:55.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她就是那樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.78,0:19:59.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}顧不上自己 總是為了什麼人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.94,0:20:02.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我去阻止她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.94,0:20:03.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:11.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我可沒能阻止 就算你和她說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:12.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.67,0:20:22.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:23.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:26.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你可能可以成功
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:30.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:34.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}失敗的話 等待你的是飛踢一百連擊的刑罰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.99,0:20:38.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.23,0:20:49.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪對新吾怎麼看的
